00:29:41,900 --> 00:29:42,780
I'm sorry.

570
00:29:43,900 --> 00:29:45,020
Don't be mad.

571
00:29:47,060 --> 00:29:48,300
You're afraid I'd be mad?

572
00:29:48,780 --> 00:29:51,260
Escort duty is a mission. I have to go.

573
00:29:53,700 --> 00:29:55,300
I never said you couldn't go,

574
00:29:56,500 --> 00:29:58,900
but why couldn't you tell me in advance?

575
00:29:59,060 --> 00:30:01,260
You knew I'm getting discharged
this September.

576
00:30:01,700 --> 00:30:02,580
And you knew clearly

577
00:30:02,580 --> 00:30:04,420
that escort duty would overlap
with that time.

578
00:30:04,900 --> 00:30:06,660
But you still chose to sign up.

579
00:30:06,940 --> 00:30:08,900
You only told me
once the list was confirmed.

580
00:30:10,460 --> 00:30:12,540
Are you trying to avoid my discharge?

581
00:30:13,500 --> 00:30:14,420
No.

582
00:30:21,940 --> 00:30:22,780
Don't worry.

583
00:30:23,260 --> 00:30:24,500
I'm a soldier too.

584
00:30:24,500 --> 00:30:25,900
I won't hold you back.

585
00:30:26,300 --> 00:30:28,420
I chose to join the army myself.

586
00:30:28,580 --> 00:30:30,740
I'll leave on my own too.

587
00:30:30,900 --> 00:30:31,580
Ke'er.

588
00:30:39,900 --> 00:30:41,180
There's no signal at sea.

589
00:30:42,740 --> 00:30:44,900
Calls have to be made
within the permitted time frame.

590
00:30:45,900 --> 00:30:47,260
I can't contact you often.

591
00:30:49,500 --> 00:30:50,300
I'm sorry.

592
00:30:51,020 --> 00:30:52,580
Take care of yourself.

593
00:30:57,580 --> 00:30:58,420
Cheng Yuan.

594
00:30:59,260 --> 00:31:00,740
Do you know what I've heard

595
00:31:00,820 --> 00:31:03,100
most often these past two years?

596
00:31:04,060 --> 00:31:05,460
It's exactly what you just said.

597
00:31:06,100 --> 00:31:07,260
"I'm sorry.

598
00:31:07,740 --> 00:31:09,660
Take care of yourself."

599
00:31:11,500 --> 00:31:12,260
What else?

600
00:31:13,004 --> 00:31:14,340
If I don't take care of myself,

601
00:31:14,340 --> 00:31:15,915
am I supposed to count on you to do it?

602
00:31:23,060 --> 00:31:23,980
Alright.

603
00:31:24,580 --> 00:31:25,500
Go back.

604
00:31:28,500 --> 00:31:30,780
Be careful while you're at sea.

605
00:32:20,700 --> 00:32:21,540
Guess who I am.

606
00:32:24,940 --> 00:32:26,100
Honey.

607
00:32:27,260 --> 00:32:28,660
Why are you back?

608
00:32:28,660 --> 00:32:29,660
I missed you.

609
00:32:33,180 --> 00:32:34,100
Alright.

610
00:32:35,740 --> 00:32:37,340
Why were you gone so long this time?

611
00:32:37,340 --> 00:32:38,780
I thought you were mad at me.

612
00:32:39,180 --> 00:32:40,740
I dare not be mad at my goddess.

613
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:41,940
Are you joking?

614
00:32:43,580 --> 00:32:44,580
I just finished training

615
00:32:44,580 --> 00:32:45,940
and didn't even get changed.

616
00:32:46,780 --> 00:32:48,260
Hurry, let me show you something.

617
00:32:51,980 --> 00:32:53,660
I went shopping today

618
00:32:53,740 --> 00:32:54,660
and bought

619
00:32:54,660 --> 00:32:56,460
some items I really like.

620
00:32:56,460 --> 00:32:57,871
You're not allowed to dislike them.

621
00:32:59,340 --> 00:33:00,300
And then,

622
00:33:00,300 --> 00:33:01,900
I don't know

623
00:33:01,900 --> 00:33:03,420
our baby's gender,

624
00:33:03,500 --> 00:33:05,420
so I bought clothes in neutral colors.

625
00:33:05,420 --> 00:33:07,580
Look. Navy blue. Is it cute?

626
00:33:13,540 --> 00:33:14,340
Honey.

627
00:33:14,782 --> 00:33:15,980
Have you thought it through?

628
00:33:18,300 --> 00:33:19,260
Yes.

629
00:33:20,020 --> 00:33:20,740
Honey.

630
00:33:21,060 --> 00:33:23,100
I'm not that scared anymore.

631
00:33:23,260 --> 00:33:25,500
Let's bring our baby into this world

632
00:33:25,660 --> 00:33:26,580
and be

633
00:33:26,580 --> 00:33:28,460
the coolest parents.

634
00:33:31,220 --> 00:33:33,660
They say pregnancy makes me silly.

635
00:33:33,820 --> 00:33:35,980
You'd better take care of me then.

636
00:33:35,980 --> 00:33:37,300
You're not allowed to say

637
00:33:37,300 --> 00:33:38,660
I've become dumb, fat,

638
00:33:38,660 --> 00:33:39,820
or ugly.

639
00:33:40,780 --> 00:33:41,980
I've thought it through.

640
00:33:42,300 --> 00:33:43,820
You'll come home once a week.

641
00:33:43,980 --> 00:33:45,060
Accompany me

642
00:33:45,060 --> 00:33:47,020
to birthing classes in the morning.

643
00:33:47,020 --> 00:33:48,260
In the afternoon,

644
00:33:48,260 --> 00:33:49,660
you'll help set up the nursery.

645
00:33:49,660 --> 00:33:50,260
Okay?

646
00:33:59,740 --> 00:34:00,340
Honey.

647
00:34:02,340 --> 00:34:03,460
I...

648
00:34:04,260 --> 00:34:07,500
was selected
for a marine escort mission abroad.

649
00:34:09,100 --> 00:34:10,180
I leave tomorrow.

650
00:34:15,540 --> 00:34:16,620
For how long?

651
00:34:19,100 --> 00:34:20,140
At least two months.

652
00:34:21,020 --> 00:34:21,940
I'm sorry.

653
00:34:22,620 --> 00:34:24,100
You'll be home by yourself again.

654
00:34:26,140 --> 00:34:27,380
It's okay.

655
00:34:27,500 --> 00:34:29,300
Mom can take care of me.

656
00:34:29,826 --> 00:34:31,782
The baby and I
will wait for you at home.

657
00:34:55,540 --> 00:34:56,340
Honey.

658
00:34:56,620 --> 00:34:57,620
Enough.

659
00:34:58,140 --> 00:35:00,020
Again? At this hour?

660
00:35:01,380 --> 00:35:02,380
What do you want to say?

661
00:35:02,820 --> 00:35:03,860
Say it to your daughter.

662
00:35:10,020 --> 00:35:10,700
Darling.

663
00:35:13,780 --> 00:35:15,020
I have to leave.

664
00:35:16,100 --> 00:35:17,540
Be good and listen to Mom.

665
00:35:17,540 --> 00:35:18,660
Don't give her a hard time.

666
00:35:20,060 --> 00:35:21,860
I'll hold you and Mom every day

667
00:35:22,620 --> 00:35:23,540
when I come back.

668
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:28,700
You

669
00:35:29,380 --> 00:35:30,620
leave in one piece,

670
00:35:31,980 --> 00:35:33,380
so come back safe and whole.

671
00:35:34,100 --> 00:35:34,980
You hear me?

672
00:35:40,860 --> 00:35:41,500
Lie down.

673
00:35:42,620 --> 00:35:43,540
Lie down.

674
00:35:43,540 --> 00:35:45,020
I'll walk you out.

675
00:35:45,020 --> 00:35:46,780
Don't. If you do,

676
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:48,700
I won't be able to leave.

677
00:35:49,250 --> 00:35:50,980
You're still playing brigadier at home?

678
00:35:51,980 --> 00:35:52,540
Be good.

679
00:36:03,260 --> 00:36:04,020
Honey.

680
00:36:06,020 --> 00:36:07,420
I'm off to handle my duty.

681
00:36:09,820 --> 00:36:11,620
Approved. Go ahead.

682
00:36:21,540 --> 00:36:22,380
Wang Lang.

683
00:36:24,860 --> 00:36:26,140
Come home soon.

684
00:36:57,500 --> 00:36:58,220
Zhaoyang.

685
00:36:59,380 --> 00:37:00,620
Why are you still up?

686
00:37:01,620 --> 00:37:02,500
Dad.

687
00:37:03,020 --> 00:37:05,020
When Mom gives birth to my sister,

688
00:37:05,020 --> 00:37:06,500
are you not going to be home?

689
00:37:14,340 --> 00:37:15,980
If I'm not home,

690
00:37:16,220 --> 00:37:17,380
will you be scared?

691
00:37:17,660 --> 00:37:18,980
No.

692
00:37:19,540 --> 00:37:21,300
Daddy, you can't be scared either.

693
00:37:21,420 --> 00:37:23,220
I already know how to take care of Mom.

694
00:37:26,315 --> 00:37:28,071
Do you remember the number of that guard

695
00:37:28,137 --> 00:37:29,380
I had you memorize?

696
00:37:30,340 --> 00:37:31,980
If Mom doesn't feel well,

697
00:37:32,180 --> 00:37:33,500
call him right away.

698
00:37:33,500 --> 00:37:34,620
He'll come and get you.

699
00:37:35,380 --> 00:37:37,500
Remember to bring Mom's maternity bag.

700
00:37:37,620 --> 00:37:38,940
It's in her closet.

701
00:37:39,140 --> 00:37:40,780
It contains toiletries

702
00:37:40,780 --> 00:37:41,940
and your sister's items.

703
00:37:42,020 --> 00:37:42,540
Also...

704
00:37:42,580 --> 00:37:44,860
I also have to bring enough cash

705
00:37:44,940 --> 00:37:47,580
and documents
like household registration book, ID,

706
00:37:47,820 --> 00:37:50,340
mother-child health records,

707
00:37:50,380 --> 00:37:51,860
birth permit,

708
00:37:52,300 --> 00:37:53,460
and medical records.

709
00:37:53,780 --> 00:37:55,820
I know all the things you tell me.

710
00:38:00,060 --> 00:38:01,140
Wang Zhaoyang.

711
00:38:01,660 --> 00:38:03,660
I'll hand over this family to you.

712
00:38:04,940 --> 00:38:06,420
Take care of your mom and sister.

713
00:38:06,460 --> 00:38:07,300
Can you do that?

714
00:38:07,660 --> 00:38:08,340
Yes!

715
00:39:00,900 --> 00:39:02,380
(Honey, you're awake?)

716
00:39:03,093 --> 00:39:04,980
(I didn't want to disturb you,
so I left first.)

717
00:39:05,060 --> 00:39:05,860
(Here's a kiss.)

718
00:39:29,048 --> 00:39:31,380
(Soy Milk Maker Manual)
(The machine in the kitchen is new.)

719
00:39:31,382 --> 00:39:33,500
(I chose the simplest one to use.)

720
00:39:33,940 --> 00:39:35,140
(I wrote notes on the manual.)

721
00:39:35,140 --> 00:39:37,060
(Please familiarize yourself
with it soon.)

722
00:39:37,060 --> 00:39:38,660
(Soy Milk Maker Instructions)

723
00:39:39,140 --> 00:39:41,700
(I got rid
of all the sodas in the fridge.)

724
00:39:41,826 --> 00:39:44,660
(No Cold Drinks! More Fruits and Milk.)
(Fruits and milk are ordered daily.)

725
00:39:44,660 --> 00:39:46,019
(They're delivered daily at noon.)

726
00:39:46,019 --> 00:39:48,560
(If you want something else,
call the number on the sticky note.)

727
00:39:51,820 --> 00:39:53,940
(I've sorted out
all the things you bought.)

728
00:39:54,220 --> 00:39:56,500
(Things you'll need soon
are right in front.)

729
00:39:56,580 --> 00:39:58,580
(Postpartum Is Easier This Way)

730
00:40:00,900 --> 00:40:02,700
(I took a few books to study.)

731
00:40:03,300 --> 00:40:05,300
(You can test me when I'm back.)

732
00:40:08,540 --> 00:40:10,300
(I disinfected the pregnancy pillow.)

733
00:40:10,500 --> 00:40:12,380
(Use it when your back hurts.)

734
00:40:16,500 --> 00:40:18,540
(The baby heart monitor
is a bit tricky.)

735
00:40:18,940 --> 00:40:20,140
(I recorded a short video.)

736
00:40:20,140 --> 00:40:21,515
(Remember to check your WeChat.)

737
00:40:33,180 --> 00:40:34,760
(Before entering the bathroom,)

738
00:40:34,782 --> 00:40:36,860
(make sure you change
into anti-slip slippers.)

739
00:40:36,915 --> 00:40:39,040
(If the anti-slip mat's dirty,
call customer support.)

740
00:40:39,220 --> 00:40:40,620
(Don't clean it yourself.)

741
00:40:41,380 --> 00:40:42,780
(I scheduled the cleaner.)

742
00:40:42,780 --> 00:40:44,820
(You're not allowed to do any chores
while I'm gone.)

743
00:40:44,820 --> 00:40:45,620
(Got it?)

744
00:40:59,826 --> 00:41:02,180
(It's my first time wrapping corners.
I'm inexperienced.)

745
00:41:02,380 --> 00:41:04,500
(I ruined the fancy drawer you bought.)

746
00:41:04,500 --> 00:41:05,580
(Please forgive me.)

747
00:41:07,820 --> 00:41:08,980
(There's no signal at sea,)

748
00:41:08,982 --> 00:41:11,380
(but I'll still greet you
good morning and night every day.)

749
00:41:11,860 --> 00:41:12,980
(Your only job)

750
00:41:12,980 --> 00:41:14,980
(is to stay healthy and gain weight.)

751
00:41:15,060 --> 00:41:16,820
(Wait at home with the baby for me.)

752
00:41:17,780 --> 00:41:19,180
(I love you both, Honey.)

753
00:41:32,220 --> 00:41:33,380
79.

754
00:41:33,580 --> 00:41:34,780
80.

755
00:41:35,060 --> 00:41:36,020
81.

756
00:41:36,700 --> 00:41:37,500
You okay?

757
00:41:37,700 --> 00:41:38,380
Get up and walk.

758
00:41:38,380 --> 00:41:40,380
The more you crouch,
the dizzier you'll feel.

759
00:41:40,900 --> 00:41:42,940
We've now reached the training sea zone.

760
00:41:42,940 --> 00:41:44,820
All members, please gather quickly.

761
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:47,500
Gather!

762
00:41:53,420 --> 00:41:54,900
Yi Nanwang, what are you doing?

763
00:41:55,580 --> 00:41:56,140
Move!

764
00:41:57,980 --> 00:41:58,660
Attention!

765
00:41:59,620 --> 00:42:01,515
Helicopter unit, prepare for flight.

766
00:42:12,901 --> 00:42:16,381
♪The vast sky and sea,
this deep blue expanse♪

767
00:42:17,071 --> 00:42:20,341
♪So deep, so boundless♪

768
00:42:20,681 --> 00:42:23,851
♪Just like your arms♪

769
00:42:24,341 --> 00:42:27,461
♪Shielding me from the dark clouds♪

770
00:42:27,751 --> 00:42:31,391
♪Always bearing it all in silence♪

771
00:42:31,391 --> 00:42:37,811
♪Even the long, long road gives me peace
when you're there♪

772
00:42:38,311 --> 00:42:42,711
♪Not one to show romance
in front of others♪

773
00:42:43,171 --> 00:42:46,261
♪You speak of dreams
with such calm simplicity♪

774
00:42:47,051 --> 00:42:51,851
♪But I know your heart
holds much deeper hopes♪

775
00:42:54,121 --> 00:42:55,961
♪I truly understand♪

776
00:42:56,451 --> 00:43:00,641
♪You speak of love so slowly♪

777
00:43:00,891 --> 00:43:06,861
♪But your eyes have already
told me everything♪

778
00:43:07,367 --> 00:43:10,057
♪Using up all my fortune♪

779
00:43:10,061 --> 00:43:14,461
♪Just to trade a lifetime with you♪

780
00:43:14,551 --> 00:43:16,771
♪Thank you for awakening♪

781
00:43:16,781 --> 00:43:21,861
♪The courage once hidden in my fear♪

782
00:43:22,001 --> 00:43:25,191
♪Turning every chance into certainty♪

783
00:43:25,521 --> 00:43:29,051
♪Turning every tie into companionship♪

784
00:43:29,131 --> 00:43:34,101
♪Blooming into brilliance
for all the years to come♪

785
00:43:34,101 --> 00:43:38,091
♪No one can tear us apart♪

786
00:43:38,281 --> 00:43:41,631
♪Each time my palm feels warmth again♪

787
00:43:41,891 --> 00:43:47,231
♪The memories return,
and I'm no longer alone♪

788
00:43:48,121 --> 00:43:52,111
♪No matter how far
across time and space♪

789
00:43:52,361 --> 00:43:55,761
♪My longing reaches you in silence♪

790
00:43:55,881 --> 00:44:00,411
♪No need to call out loudly♪

791
00:44:00,411 --> 00:44:03,081
♪No matter how much it takes♪

792
00:44:03,101 --> 00:44:07,511
♪To bring this drifting heart to shore♪

793
00:44:07,511 --> 00:44:10,771
♪Thank you for standing behind me♪

794
00:44:10,791 --> 00:44:14,841
♪Lighting up the darkness and despair♪

795
00:44:14,841 --> 00:44:18,311
♪The bigger the world,
the lonelier it feels♪

796
00:44:18,311 --> 00:44:22,081
♪Only by your side♪

797
00:44:22,091 --> 00:44:29,171
♪Can I truly feel this warmth inside♪
